The exact transformation, distilled
Ignoring comment edits and the UUID suffixes I changed only to keep the two files distinguishable, the real changes per row are exactly two:
1. Delete the static dots <staticText> element. For example:
xml<staticText>
    <reportElement x="240" y="0" width="204" height="14" uuid="d279da75-..."/>
    <text><![CDATA[......................................]]></text>
</staticText>
→ removed entirely.
2. Replace the value field's expression from
xml<textFieldExpression><![CDATA[$F{customerName}]]></textFieldExpression>
to
xml<textFieldExpression><![CDATA[($F{customerName} == null ? "" : $F{customerName}) + "........................................................................................................................................................................................................".substring(0, Math.max(3, Math.min(200, 71 - ($F{customerName} == null ? 0 : $F{customerName}.length()))))]]></textFieldExpression>